<HEADLINE> Xinhua Stock Indexes Change Mixedly </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, June 22 (Xinhua) -- Today's Xinhua A stock index
fell by 1.64 points to close at 170.18, while the Xinhua B
stock index edged up 0.09 point to finish at 43.72.
</P>
<P>
The Xinhua Stock Index is China's first national unitary stock
exponent, which is jointly designed and issued by the Economic
Information Department of the Xinhua News Agency and Beijing
University.  
