<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, June 22 (Xinhua) -- The United States has now become
one of the largest sources of direct overseas investment in China,
said Sun Zhengyu, vice-minister of foreign trade and economic
cooperation, here this morning.
</P>
<P>
To the end of last May, actual U.S. investment in China had
exceeded 18 billion U.S. dollars, with a total of 24,000
enterprises registered here since the country's reform and
opening-up first introduced two decades ago, Sun said at a press
conference sponsored the Information Office of the State Council.
</P>
<P>
