<TEXT>
<P>
CHENGDU, June 22 (Xinhua) -- An Expressway built jointly by
Sichuan Province, southwest China, and Hong Kong developers has
been cited as a model for efficiently recovering investment.
</P>
<P>
Though the Chengdu-Mianyang Expressway is only 80 percent
completed, it has been generating income because it is the first
expressway in the province to become operational before the whole
project is completed.
</P>
